RACE
This is a two player racing game built in OpenGL using features like colliding physics, textures,
lighting(specular and diffused), shadowing etc. The controls for this game is given below.

CONTROLS

1 -> driver view
2 -> rooftop view
3 -> sliding box view
4 -> search light view
5 -> wheel view
6 -> overhead view
7 -> helicopter cam
8 -> top view

___left car___
a -> turns left
d -> turns right
w -> accelerates
s -> decelerates

___right car___
LEFT_BUTTON -> turns left
RIGHT_BUTTON -> turns right
UP_BUTTON -> accelerates
DOWN_BUTTON -> decelerates

q -> sunrise
e -> sunset

+ -> increase ambient intensity
- -> decrease ambient intensity

o -> toggle fog
i -> increase fog intensity
p -> decrease fog intensity

z,x -> pillar properties

c -> toggle diffused property
v -> toggle specular property
b -> toggle emissive property
